_sText:
This is the final version and hopefully there won't be any bugs, if so leave a comment saying where the bug is and i will be sure to fix it and update the map download(On the same page).

The map has the original Minecraft background noise.
I have added sounds to all the traps that needed them.
From the last version the second level(Neather) was to dark and made it alot brighter so people don't have to use there flash lights.
There are a total of 14 traps and there a 6 fun nades to be found.

Overall i think this is a enjoyable map for people to play as its not to long and not to short and has originality to it. HAVE FUN!
